#NoToBushiriExtradition Black First Land First (BLF) will hand deliver a letter of appeal to the Malawian government, asking it to respect the rights of Prophet and Prophetess Bushiri. A media briefing and reading of the letter shall be done after delivery of the letter under the following details: 1. Date: 4th March 2021
2. Time: 11am
3. Venue: 770 Government Avenue, Arcadia, Pretoria Issued by Black First Land First, National Coordinating Committee (BLF NCC)
3 March 2021 Contact Details Black First Land First Mail: blackfirstlandfirst@gmail.com Zanele Lwana
(BLF Deputy President)
Cell: +27 79 986 7225 Reposted from the BLF website.